    "description": "Survive hordes of enemies in this roguelite action game by managing spells and finding what works best for you in different situations. Defeat monsters, collect their drops and return to your campsite to craft gear and unlock new spells to make following runs easier!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242440/extras/96e4cf6979bdb149f1a1f1334e04f226.webp?t=1721698582\" width=600 height=28 /></span><li><strong>Levels</strong><br>Defeat the incoming enemies in different environments and survive long enough to face the final boss of the level, and collect the materials dropped by defeated enemies to craft new gear and unlock spells.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242440/extras/96e4cf6979bdb149f1a1f1334e04f226.webp?t=1721698582\" width=600 height=28 /></span><br></li><li><strong>The Shop</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242440/extras/ce176fc965ad8b3dc1f9313239462454.poster.avif?t=1721698582\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242440/extras/ce176fc965ad8b3dc1f9313239462454.webm?t=1721698582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242440/extras/ce176fc965ad8b3dc1f9313239462454.mp4?t=1721698582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>After each wave you have a Shop break where you can buy new spells, upgrade your gear and buy spells you already have to upgrade them. Choosing what to buy each break is key in preparing for the waves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242440/extras/96e4cf6979bdb149f1a1f1334e04f226.webp?t=1721698582\" width=600 height=28 /></span><br></li><li><strong>The Campsite</strong><br>The campsite is your base of operations, here you can check your materials, craft new gear and unlock new spells to help you in future runs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242440/extras/96e4cf6979bdb149f1a1f1334e04f226.webp?t=1721698582\" width=600 height=28 /></span><br></li><li><strong>Different Playstyles</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242440/extras/9fc5b3a1367cfad689937f3fdc35a470.poster.avif?t=1721698582\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242440/extras/9fc5b3a1367cfad689937f3fdc35a470.webm?t=1721698582\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242440/extras/9fc5b3a1367cfad689937f3fdc35a470.mp4?t=1721698582\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Crafting and equipping armor not only changes your look, but also activates skills that change your playstyle, collect materials in each run to craft your favorite gear and create your own loadout and look.</li></ul>",
